.TH LOA-READING-SMART-APPEND 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
reading smart append \- Append smart recommendations to reading list
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> reading smart append
.br
alexandria> reading smart append 5
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Builds recommendation candidates and appends them to the existing reading list.
.TP
Already listed books are not duplicated.
.TP
Optional count controls how many recommendations are considered (default: 10).
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> reading smart append
.TP
alexandria> reading smart append 4
